ZH: 我每天早上都会梳洗头发。
EN: I brush and wash my hair every morning.

ZH: 他忘了梳洗而匆忙地离开了家。
EN: He left home in a hurry and forgot to groom himself.

ZH: 她在镜子前梳洗了一下才去上学。
EN: She groomed herself in front of the mirror before going to school.

ZH: 孩子们在早上梳洗完毕后迎接新的一天。
EN: The children welcome a new day after grooming in the morning.

ZH: 我常常在梳洗的时候想些事情。
EN: I often think about things while grooming.

ZH: 她喜欢在浴室里慢慢梳洗。
EN: She likes to take her time grooming in the bathroom.

ZH: 梳洗后，他准备出门上班。
EN: After grooming, he is ready to go to work.

ZH: 在夏天，人们特别喜欢梳洗凉爽的沐浴露。
EN: People especially like to use refreshing shower gel when grooming in summer.

ZH: 我每天晚上都要梳洗才能入睡。
EN: I need to groom myself every night before I can fall asleep.

ZH: 她一边慢慢梳洗头发，一边听音乐放松自己。
EN: She relaxes herself by listening to music while slowly grooming her hair.

ZH: 洗完澡后就可以开始梳洗头发了。
EN: After taking a shower, you can start grooming your hair.

ZH: 梳洗的时候，我发现了一些头皮屑。
EN: While grooming, I discovered some dandruff.

ZH: 他每天早上都喜欢在梳洗的时候听雷鬼音乐。
EN: He enjoys listening to reggae music while grooming every morning.

ZH: 为了给自己一个良好的心情，她每天都会精心梳洗。
EN: To give herself a good mood, she grooms herself carefully every day.

ZH: 她每天都要花很多时间梳洗才满意。
EN: She spends a lot of time grooming herself every day until she is satisfied.

ZH: 即使很疲倦，我也会梳洗扮漂亮参加晚宴。
EN: Even when I am tired, I will groom myself and dress nicely for the dinner party.

ZH: 梳洗是一天开始的第一步。
EN: Grooming is the first step to start the day.

ZH: 他的马在比赛前梳洗得干净整齐。
EN: His horse is groomed and clean before the race.

ZH: 每个人出门前都应该梳洗整理仪容。
EN: Everyone should groom and tidy themselves up before going out.

ZH: 我们一家人都喜欢在梳洗之后一起吃早餐。
EN: Our family likes to have breakfast together after grooming.

ZH: 她细心地梳洗并为自己打上了精致的妆容。
EN: She carefully groomed herself and put on exquisite makeup.
